            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>光洋科(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1785:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1785\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1785-TW</a>)27日10:01上漲8.7元，股價漲停報96.4元，委買17,229,000張，成交44,182張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為貴金屬材料。鑄錠。其他。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>光洋科(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1785:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1785\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1785-TW</a>)近5日股價下跌13.6%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌2.12%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-5,548 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-4,902 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：+3 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-649 張</li> <li>融資增減：-4,814 張</li> <li>融券增減：+265 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
