            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>信錦(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1582:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1582\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1582-TW</a>)27日10:04上漲9元，股價漲停報102.0元，委買133張、委賣2,929張，成交16,851張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為樞紐HINGE之製造及買賣。各種模具之加工製造及買賣。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>信錦(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1582:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1582\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1582-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲0.32%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌1.05%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+2,596 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+2,740 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-144 張</li> <li>融資增減：-120 張</li> <li>融券增減：-36 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
